OSLO ASSET MANAGEMENT
OUR OBJECTIVE: Develop sustainable investment strategies that can generate consistent investment returns independent of economic cycles
OUR EDGE: Combining industry knowledge, in-depth fundamental research and capital market expertise in order to consistently exploit absolute and relative valuation inefficiencies
OUR STRATEGY: Specialized investment strategy dedicated to exploiting fundamental inefficiencies in publicly traded securities globally within energy and natural resources
OUR VALUES: Knowledge, Integrity, Dedication and Discipline. Our core values are reflected in our individual aspirations and demonstrated by the way we conduct our business









 



 












