Business:
Asset Management

Asset ManagementReturn to Savings and InvestmentsDNB Asset Management is a leading financial institution in the Nordic region that provides tailored investment solutions across a variety of asset classes to retail and institutional clients. We employ skilled and incentivised specialist managers who are supported by an established, stable and focused organization.International fund range?If you are an investor operating in continental Europe or any other destination, we encourage you to visit our International website. DNB has a full range of Luxembourg domiciled funds set up to service the professional investment community.» Please visit our DNB International WebsiteDNB Asset Management
DNB Asset Management ranks among the top 5 managers in the Nordic regionMore than 550 000 mutual fund customers in Norway and 300 institutional clients in Norway, Sweden and Continental Europe *
75 portfolio managers and analysts with more than 61 billion EUR under management *
A global manager with offices in Oslo, Stockholm, Bergen, and Luxembourg.
The asset manager integrates SRI screening across all investment strategies
We offer a broad range of investment products across various asset classes under the brand name DNB, formerly also known as DNB NOR, Avanse and Carlson.

Feel free to contact us if you have any enquiries about our DNB range of funds.See also: » International fund range» Norwegian funds» About the DNB Group   FacebookTwitterGoogle+PrintContact usMon-Fri 08.00 - 16.00 CET+47 22 47 40 00E-mailFax: +47 24 05 03 00Visiting address:Dronning Eufemias gate 30Mailing address:N-0021 Oslo 

